{
  "id": "fyEosQzE",
  "slug": "exploration-more",
  "title": "Exploration & More",
  "description": "This modpack focuses on exploration and survival. These two aspects are paired with the awesome Create Mod.",
  "body": "<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mlMucn9.jpg\" alt=\"Exploration & More\" />\n    <hr />\n    <p>\n      This modpack focuses on exploration and survival. These two aspects are\n      paired with the awesome\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric\">Create Mod</a>.\n    </p>\n    <hr />\n    <p>The main features are:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>🧭 Exploration specific loot</li>\n      <li>🌍 Reworked Overworld</li>\n      <li>🌋 Reworked Nether</li>\n      <li>🌐 Reworked End</li>\n      <li>🍔 Overhauled food and health system</li>\n      <li>🔆 Seasons and climate effects</li>\n      <li>🐉 Some Bosses & special Mobs</li>\n      <li>✨ All the performance mods you know</li>\n    </ul>\n    <hr />\n    <p>Important:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>The modpack is tested with 5GB RAM. However, 8 GB is recommended.</li>\n      <li>\n        Iris & Flywheel Compat is disabled by default because it can cause\n        crashes. You can enable it but be warned.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n    <hr />\n    <p>Notes:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/simple-backup\">Simple Backup</a> is\n        disabled by default. To enable it go to your config folder and open\n        'simplebackup.json5'. Set 'enableAutomaticBackups' and\n        'enableServerStoppedBackup' to true. The backups are saved in your games\n        folder in 'simpleBackup'\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The modpack is shader ready. Simply install the shader of your choice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The gamerules doPatrolSpawning, mobGriefing, doFireTick and doInsomnia\n        are set to false by default.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n    <hr />\n    <p>Thanks:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Thanks to everyone from the\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs\">KubeJS</a> team and the KubeJS\n        extensions teams. Your mods are just awesome.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n    <hr />\n    <details>\n      <summary>Download Recommendations</summary>\n      <ul>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/os-cleaner-signs\"\n            >Os' Cleaner Signs</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/os-colorful-grasses\"\n            >Os' Colorful Grasses</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/artisanal-default\"\n            >Artisanal Default</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/simple-grass-flowers\"\n            >Simple Grass Flowers</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/os-shulkers\"\n            >Os' Shulkers</a\n          >\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </details>\n    <hr />\n    <details>\n      <summary>Modlist</summary>\n      <!-- permisson -->\n      <ul>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aquamirae\">Aquamirae</a>\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/controlling\">Controlling</a></li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cottagecraft-axolotls\"\n            >CottageCraft Axolotls</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dehydration\">Dehydration</a></li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dripsounds-fabric\"\n            >Drip Sounds (Fabric)</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/environmentz\">EnviromentZ</a></li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/explorers-compass\"\n            >Explorers Compass</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/extended-drawers\"\n            >Extended Drawers</a\n          >\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/extraalchemy\">Extra Alchemy</a>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fallin